name: Contrast within city
description: There's a place in Seoul that has a lot of metal, electronics, machine parts, tool shop. It's one of Seoul's oldest market and this place is getting closer to getting demolished day by day. People here are old, powerless, dying generation, but behind this picture in the skyscrapers and buildings, they will get these people's properties and make more money out of it. / Format : Jpeg / Size : 6000x3243
